    {
      "id": "poem-moshang-001",
      "title": "七律·夜阑",
      "category": "文学诗歌",
      "date": "2025-06-01",
      "readTime": 3,
      "excerpt": "采梌几尝风雨意，孤身一往天涯人。",
      "image": "",
      "content": "<div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;\">\n\n<p style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:0.95rem;font-style:italic;color:#9e9284;letter-spacing:0.06em;margin-bottom:3rem;\">— 吕庭锐</p>\n\n<table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:3.5rem;\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:1.6rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;color:#18160f;padding:0.55rem 0;white-space:nowrap;\">陌上潇潇杜宇去，</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:1.6rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;color:#18160f;padding:0.55rem 0;white-space:nowrap;\">月下悄悄夏虫吟。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:0.4rem 0;\"></td></tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:1.6rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;color:#18160f;padding:0.55rem 0;white-space:nowrap;\">采梌几尝风雨意，</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:1.6rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;color:#18160f;padding:0.55rem 0;white-space:nowrap;\">孤身一往天涯人。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:0.4rem 0;\"></td></tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:1.6rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;color:#18160f;padding:0.55rem 0;white-space:nowrap;\">云深路遥憯不明，</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:1.6rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;color:#18160f;padding:0.55rem 0;white-space:nowrap;\">枯草落花朽柴门。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:0.4rem 0;\"></td></tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:1.6rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;color:#18160f;padding:0.55rem 0;white-space:nowrap;\">残漏不解天地阔，</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:1.6rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;color:#18160f;padding:0.55rem 0;white-space:nowrap;\">几声将断几声深。</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none;border-top:1px solid rgba(24,22,15,0.08);margin:2.8rem 0;\"/>\n\n<p style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.64rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#7c4db8;margin-bottom:1.8rem;\">English rendering</p>\n\n<table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:2.5rem;\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:1.08rem;font-style:italic;color:#3a3428;padding:0.42rem 0;white-space:nowrap;\">The cuckoo leaves the windswept path, its cry grown thin,</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:1.08rem;font-style:italic;color:#3a3428;padding:0.42rem 0;white-space:nowrap;\">Beneath the moon, summer insects hum their requiem.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:0.35rem 0;\"></td></tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:1.08rem;font-style:italic;color:#3a3428;padding:0.42rem 0;white-space:nowrap;\">I have gathered what wind and rain were trying to say,</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:1.08rem;font-style:italic;color:#3a3428;padding:0.42rem 0;white-space:nowrap;\">And alone, pressed onward to the edge of the world away.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:0.35rem 0;\"></td></tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:1.08rem;font-style:italic;color:#3a3428;padding:0.42rem 0;white-space:nowrap;\">Cloud-deep, road-long — grief too dark to name or see,</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:1.08rem;font-style:italic;color:#3a3428;padding:0.42rem 0;white-space:nowrap;\">Withered grass, fallen petals, a rotting gate — and me.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:0.35rem 0;\"></td></tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:1.08rem;font-style:italic;color:#3a3428;padding:0.42rem 0;white-space:nowrap;\">The failing clepsydra cannot fathom how vast the sky —</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:1.08rem;font-style:italic;color:#3a3428;padding:0.42rem 0;white-space:nowrap;\">A few drops nearly spent, a few more sinking dry.</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p style=\"font-family:'EB Garamond',serif;font-size:0.88rem;font-style:italic;color:#a09284;line-height:1.9;border-top:1px solid rgba(24,22,15,0.06);padding-top:1.6rem;\"><em>Notes —</em> 杜宇: the cuckoo; in classical verse its cry carries the ache of those who cannot return home. 残漏: a clepsydra, the water-clock that marks time drop by drop — here nearly spent, yet blind to the immensity it has outlasted.</p>\n\n</div>"
    },
